TopicTitle: 'Muppets' low-partcount medium and heavy lifter series

Articles.Content:
So the topic of Sesame Street popped up on IRC, prompting Rokker to say that Muppets would be a cool thing to name rockets after. I shamelessly stole this idea.

> [Javascript is disabled. View full album](//imgur.com/a/JIfRl)

BigBird-Core medium lift: 20t to LKO, in less than ten parts

> [Javascript is disabled. View full album](//imgur.com/a/Sr44E)

Big Bird-5 long lift: 20t to Mun orbit, in less than twenty parts

> [Javascript is disabled. View full album](//imgur.com/a/A9vNO)

Snuffleufagus heavy lifter: 100t to LKO, 59 parts
